==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''Ancient Greek'''

The [[Greek]] language from the earliest records ([[Creto-Mycenaean language]], [[Linear B]] inscriptions, about 1600-1300 BCE) to about 300 BCE, including the main dialects [[Aeolic]], [[Arcadic]], [[Doric]], and [[Ionic]].

